466cff176d05597bceb1c4b3bb114263177b7a19","tid":1459311,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6eb275a78d24c7d60f60a229a52710b29384f60","tid":1459311,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6958de9e5f430aa07fe61d5cc8a6bd6ac8a536e","tid":1459311,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"其實我有個建議 就係前線組小隊 互相比自己ig fb 小隊入面既人check 伸報自己職業 最好帶埋自己職業既證明 或者學生show 學生證"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"D狗可以整假身份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:16:38.000Z","msg":"睇返曬我既reply"},{"pid":"e8cc1b8870d3a37ae17c7f99b8f17b96fadfb407","tid":1459311,"uid":295190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"少少講一聲<br />\n利申我覺得係可行嘅<br />\n只係真係要小心求証<br />\n香港政府插針可能只係一時半載<br />\n中共插針係以年計嘅<br />\n所以求証可以嘅話求証到底最穩陣"},{"pid":"5298b08c02be9616e56eee1c536fc285ea039c77","tid":1459311,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"暫時唔好做d臨場帶到風向既行動<br />\n例如去邊度<br />\n<br />\n一開始有明確目標<br />\n唔可以帶耳筒"},{"pid":"6efa7e3102efd4cbd59ad2d648e943c89221c1fe","tid":1459311,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:40:52.000Z","msg":"唔須要再講任何解釋，已進入戰爭狀態，要刺客隊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武唔好再出黎遊行，全部自組搵仔<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以500隻狗為短期目標<br />\n<br />\n例子:何母山墳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">其他機場文宣，記者會屌狗，大遊行，和理非會負責</span></span>"},{"pid":"90dceb1ef3cecb66207e0065fb0bae0c8c3c7313","tid":1459311,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:04:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0beb8bbdac9f0064ec3ed1744490072351c85047","tid":1459311,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63a3dbde369e859267c3667d72bda1b991cab535","tid":1459311,"uid":